{"tid":579441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唉，同老婆搬番屋企又要受氣","createTime":"2018-03-03T15:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T15:34:34.000Z","uid":57035,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"73e8e426a9aceeec7e5ad66b1626a4b838188ef6","tid":579441,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前同老婆搬出去就唔想日日對面我哥同我媽<br />\n因為做左爸爸,為個仔份上(而家六個月)<br />\n咪搬返去住,起碼有屋企人照顧下我老婆<br />\n點知我阿哥(離左婚有個仔一齊住)<br />\n成日話我老婆唔幫我媽做下家務<br />\n又成日出街或者係房訓唔幫手<br />\n大佬呀 28週仲想點呀 <br />\n今日佢放假 以為我老婆出左街 其實我老婆係房<br />\n聽到我哥咁講野<br />\n「係到話老婆 唔幫手做野頭先我老婆又唔識拜神個d野<br />\n咁我媽又唔叫老婆幫手<br />\n話我老婆坐係到咩都唔理」<br />\n之後又叫我無啦啦比多5千蚊家用佢供樓<br />\n自問bb出世買左好多野 人工得1k4 仲要搭車(屯門去東涌返工) 保險(我同老婆各份)<br />\n每個月比埋佢 得1千蚊淨 唔好話儲留黎比bb用呀<br />\n我媽最過份有次我岳母衝口而出 問層居屋 死左會唔會比我<br />\n點知我媽都話淨比我哥 我屌<br />\n家下我比d家用 我又無得分層樓 仲要我比咁多做咩<br />\n呢幾星期就係為左d野鬱埋鬱埋<br />\n我老婆係屋企成日又唔開心 <br />\n搞到呢排佢訓唔著 我又被佢影響到自己都無咩精神<br />\n本身搬返黎原因係有次我老婆話下體流血 我call白車<br />\n點知佢地個編號同我住個唐樓編號唔同<br />\n搞到好擔心 同有個孫我老母同阿哥都唔會咁衰<br />\n點知家下又好似以為咁<br />\nps:之前搬出去係因為同我哥嘈大鑊 又係同上面d野差唔多"},{"pid":"8ae44eb2bac55351b5d8248d92dfb473dd52aab5","tid":579441,"uid":130901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:23:43.000Z","msg":"只可以話，大嫂好好醒走得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66de95de133706669edee530c0b0b8e29e724fe","tid":579441,"uid":1060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"去娘家度住囉<br />\n而家好興嫁啦 唔洗擔心"},{"pid":"8b9ac7a1027325359bb31826b044e2ad22fd256d","tid":579441,"uid":108353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:24:33.000Z","msg":"叫老婆返娘家安胎再算"},{"pid":"68f49b348e90c89a46d29572d81c269d3a0f78cf","tid":579441,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:26:28.000Z","msg":"篇文邊度copy嫁？"},{"pid":"7a99a833b46a9a21345ac963b9e3891cf87a87a7","tid":579441,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"14k per month?<br />\n咁都夠膽生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba58b01390d785fadaa8246fb0f278d2cd4f9a8","tid":579441,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a99a833b46a9a21345ac963b9e3891cf87a87a7","tid":579441,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"14k per month?<br />\n咁都夠膽生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:28:35.000Z","msg":"計過數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b490265be1bb622a653da66d43701981966bd6","tid":579441,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:29:40.000Z","msg":"你老婆咁熟口面嘅"},{"pid":"6bc347a4560524aeeb209b64280619ec584d71d7","tid":579441,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:34:34.000Z","msg":"抄post有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}